name: DarkStar
description: DarkStar is a fun, cross-platform space game blending Web2 and Web3. It's an airplane level-breaking game and very easy to get start - players can simply enjoy the adventures through battles, boss fights, auto-cruising and more, they can use upgrade the spaceship to keep engaged The embedded real-time AI systems for dynamic gameplay, including AI-assisted missions and personalized strategies enable players to have unique experience.
